---
const steps = [
	{
		title: '1. Tell us the matter',
		copy: 'Choose the service lane, answer the fit questions, and share only the core facts the firm needs first.',
	},
	{
		title: '2. The request is reviewed',
		copy: 'New matters are screened for fit, urgency, conflicts, and current availability before the next step is offered.',
	},
	{
		title: '3. You get the next step',
		copy: 'If it fits, the next move is usually an email with scheduling instructions and the $100 30-minute consultation link.',
	},
];
---

<div class="panel intake-panel">
	<p class="mini-kicker">3-Step Intake Path</p>
	<h2 class="mini-title">How requests usually move.</h2>
	<ol class="intake-steps">
		{
			steps.map((step) => (
				<li>
					<strong>{step.title}</strong>
					<span>{step.copy}</span>
				</li>
			))
		}
	</ol>
	<p class="mini-copy">Most requests are reviewed within 1 business day when submitted on a business day.</p>
</div>
